properties.script:
/**
 * @summary Transforms the provided input record into zero or more output records or errors.

 * Input records are available in JavaScript code as JSON objects. 

 * @param input an object that contains the input record as a JSON.   e.g. to access a field called 'total' from the input record, use input.total.
 * @param emitter an object that can be used to emit zero or more records (using the emitter.emit() method) or errors (using the emitter.emitError() method) 
 * @param context an object that provides access to:
 *            1. CDAP Metrics - context.getMetrics().count('output', 1);
 *            2. CDAP Logs - context.getLogger().debug('Received a record');
 *            3. Lookups - context.getLookup('blacklist').lookup(input.id); or
 *            4. Runtime Arguments - context.getArguments().get('priceThreshold') 
 */ 
function transform(input, emitter, context) { // Added emitter and context
    var isPaid = input.ispaid != null ? input.ispaid : false;
    var chargetypeid = input.chargetypeid != null ? input.chargetypeid : 0;
    
       var paymentChargeTypeIds = [
        // Core Customer Payments
        1006, // Lease Rental
        1007, // Loan Repayment
        1008, // Loan Repayment - Interest
        1010, // Secondary Period Lease Rentals
        1012, // Advance Loan/HP Repayment-Interest
        1013, // Advance Lease Repayment - Rental
        1014, // Advance Lease Repayment - Interest
        1031, // Precommencement Interest
        1036, // Late Payment Interest
        1045, // Extension Interest
        1050, // Lease Rental Interest
        1052, // Advance Rental
        1058, // Late Fee
        1210, // Downpayment
        1219, // Capitalized Cost Reduction
        1220, // Security Deposit
        1615, // Daily Extension Fee

        // Customer Fees & Charges
        1211, // Documentation Fee - Retail
        1212, // Documentation Fee - Lease
        1213, // Title, License & Reg. Fees - Retail
        1214, // Title, License & Reg. Fees - Lease
        1221, // Lease Acquisition Fee (Up-Front)
        1224, // Administration Fee
        1225, // In-life Administration Fee
        1510, // Non Sufficient Funds Fee
        1611, // Disposition Fee
        1612, // Excess Wear & Tear Fee
        1923, // Filing Fee - Lease
        1924, // Filing Fee - Retail
        1925, // Upfront Taxes - Lease
        1926, // Upfront Taxes - Retail
        1059, // Excess Mileage Charge

        // Ancillary Products (Payments for optional services)
        1105, // GAP Insurance - Retail
        1106, // GAP Insurance - Lease
        1107, // Prepaid Maintenance - Retail
        1108, // Prepaid Maintenance - Lease
        1109, // Extended Warranty Plan - Retail
        1110, // Extended Warranty Plan - Lease
        1111, // Credit Life Insurance - Retail
        1112, // Credit Life Insurance - Lease
        1121, // Excess Wear & Tear (as a product)
        1122, // Physical Damage Insurance
        1927, // WearCare
        1929  // In Life Extended Warranty
    ];
    if (!(isPaid && paymentChargeTypeIds.indexOf(chargetypeid) !== -1)) {
        return; // Filter out records by not calling emitter.emit()
    }

    emitter.emit({ // Changed from 'return' to 'emitter.emit'
        scheduleid: input.scheduleid,
        id_count: 1
    });
}
